# Cursor AI Project Prompt & Rules

## Project Overview

Build a modern Android task management application with Kanban board, notes system, and media management following the latest Android best practices.

---

## Core Requirements

### Application Purpose
- Task/Todo management system with Kanban-style board
- Rich note-taking with organization features
- Comprehensive media manager
- Smart AI-powered task breakdown notifications
- Gamification for productivity

### Main Features
1. **Kanban Board** with collapsible sections (Personal, Work, Family)
2. **Notes System** with rich text formatting, tags, and attachments
3. **Media Manager** with grid/list views and navigation to source
4. **Smart Notifications** using ML for task breakdown
5. **Task Details** with checklists, progress tracking, and rich formatting

---

## Multi-Module Architecture (Feature Modules)

### Project Structure Overview

```
project-root/
├── app/                           // Main app module (minimal, orchestration only)
├── core/
│   ├── common/                    // Shared utilities, extensions
│   ├── design-system/             // UI components, theme, Material3
│   ├── data/                      // Data layer abstractions
│   ├── database/                  // Room database, DAOs
│   ├── network/                   // Retrofit, API clients (if needed)
│   └── model/                     // Shared domain models
├── feature/
│   ├── kanban/                    // Kanban board feature
│   ├── notes/                     // Notes feature
